{
  "info": {
    "name": "ClickEscola — API Gateway",
    "description": "Coleção que exercita o gateway (http://localhost:8080) cobrindo os itens obrigatórios: roteamento, 2 serviços por entrada única, logs/tempo de resposta, comparação direto vs. gateway e tratamento de erro. Use a variável {{gateway}}.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "gateway", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "direto_cursos", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "aluno_id", "value": "" },
    { "key": "curso_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. Health do gateway",
      "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{gateway}}/health", "host": ["{{gateway}}"], "path": ["health"] } }
    },
    {
      "name": "1. Criar aluno (FastAPI)",
      "event": [
        { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
          "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.code === 201);",
          "const id = pm.response.json().id;",
          "if (id) pm.collectionVariables.set('aluno_id', id);",
          "console.log('X-Request-ID:', pm.response.headers.get('X-Request-ID'));"
        ], "type": "text/javascript" } }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"nome\": \"Maria Silva\",\n  \"email\": \"maria@escola.edu\",\n  \"matricula\": \"2024001\"\n}" },
        "url": { "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/alunos", "host": ["{{gateway}}"], "path": ["api", "alunos"] }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Listar alunos",
      "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/alunos", "host": ["{{gateway}}"], "path": ["api", "alunos"] } }
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Buscar aluno por id",
      "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/alunos/{{aluno_id}}", "host": ["{{gateway}}"], "path": ["api", "alunos", "{{aluno_id}}"] } }
    },
    {
      "name": "4. Criar curso (NestJS)",
      "event": [
        { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
          "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.code === 201);",
          "const id = pm.response.json().id;",
          "if (id) pm.collectionVariables.set('curso_id', id);",
          "console.log('X-Request-ID:', pm.response.headers.get('X-Request-ID'));"
        ], "type": "text/javascript" } }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"nome\": \"Engenharia de Software\",\n  \"carga_horaria\": 3600\n}" },
        "url": { "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/cursos", "host": ["{{gateway}}"], "path": ["api", "cursos"] }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "5. Listar cursos",
      "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/cursos", "host": ["{{gateway}}"], "path": ["api", "cursos"] } }
    },
    {
      "name": "6. Buscar curso por id",
      "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/cursos/{{curso_id}}", "host": ["{{gateway}}"], "path": ["api", "cursos", "{{curso_id}}"] } }
    },
    {
      "name": "7. Acesso DIRETO ao cursos (requer override da porta)",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "description": "Só funciona se a porta direta estiver exposta (demo override). Mostra que o acesso direto NÃO tem X-Request-ID nem passa pelo log/rate-limit do gateway.",
        "url": { "raw": "{{direto_cursos}}/cursos", "host": ["{{direto_cursos}}"], "path": ["cursos"] }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "8. Erro tratado (rode após 'docker stop service-cursos')",
      "event": [
        { "listen": "test", "script": { "exec": [
          "pm.test('503 tratado pelo gateway', () => pm.response.code === 503);",
          "pm.test('corpo JSON amigável', () => pm.response.json().error !== undefined);"
        ], "type": "text/javascript" } }
      ],
      "request": { "method": "GET", "header": [], "url": { "raw": "{{gateway}}/api/cursos", "host": ["{{gateway}}"], "path": ["api", "cursos"] } }
    }
  ]
}
